---
// Components Imports
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";

// Assets Imports
import { BSShowcase, BSStyle } from "@/assets";
---

<Layout
  description='Woocommerce Headless created with Next.js, Next-Auth, and WordPress for selling padel items'
  title='Backswing - Woocommerce Headless'
  label='Projects'
  link='/es/works'
  border='border-gray-800'>
  <main
    class='w-screen mt-20 md:mt-10 md:px-24 relative flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-10 md:gap-20'>
    <div class='w-full bg-gray-950 text-center h-[700px] flex justify-center'>
      <h1
        class='font-prata text-[11vw] text-gray-100 self-center md:self-end md:leading-[11rem]'>
        BACKSWING
      </h1>
    </div>
    <h2
      class='text-[7vw] md:text-[3vw] font-prata max-w-[700px] md:leading-[4rem] my-10 px-5 md:p-0'>
       Woocommerce Headless for selling padel items, using Next.js as the application base and these technologies:
    </h2>
    <div
      class='flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-3 md:gap-5 md:px-10 px-5'>
      <div class='flex-1 space-y-2'>
        <h3 class='font-bold md:text-lg'>Next.js</h3>
        <p class='text-sm md:text-base'>
          Used by some of the world's largest companies, Next.js allows you to create complete web applications by extending the latest React features and integrating powerful JavaScript tools based on Rust for the fastest builds.
        </p>
        <a
          href='https://astro.build/'
          target='_blank'
          class='hover-underline-animation text-sm font-bold'>More info.</a
        >
      </div>
      <div class='flex-1 space-y-2'>
        <h3 class='font-bold md:text-lg'>Next-Auth</h3>
        <p class='text-sm md:text-base'>
          User data processing, authentication, authorization, and provider authentication.
        </p>
        <a
          href='https://authjs.dev/'
          target='_blank'
          class='hover-underline-animation text-sm font-bold'>More info.</a
        >
      </div>
      <div class='flex-1 space-y-2'>
        <h3 class='font-bold md:text-lg'>Woocommerce</h3>
        <p class='text-sm md:text-base'>
          Woocommerce is an e-commerce system for online commerce for WordPress.
        </p>
        <a
          href='https://woocommerce.com/en/'
          target='_blank'
          class='hover-underline-animation text-sm font-bold'>More info.</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <img src={BSShowcase.src} alt='Backswing Website Showcase' />
    <p class='max-w-[800px] px-5 md:px-0 text-sm md:text-base'>
      For this site, the goal was to create a storefront that was fast, customizable, and functional to meet the client's expectations. We chose Next.js as the application's foundation, integrating shdcn and Tailwind CSS to optimize the interface and user experience.

We used WordPress and WooCommerce for the backend store due to their great capacity for setting up a virtual store and ease of learning. We added some plugins to enhance this interaction, such as JWT for authorization and Headless to ensure it is exclusively used by the client.
    </p>
    <img src={BSStyle.src} alt='Backswing Website Style' />
  </main>
  <div
    class='fixed bottom-10 right-10 p-3 md:p-5 text-left rounded-lg space-y-2 bg-gray-950'>
    <a
      href='https://github.com/N4N1T0/backswing-ecommerce'
      target='_blank'
      class='text-sm md:text-base hover-underline-animation-widget'>CODE</a
    >
    <a
      href='https://backswing-ecommerce.vercel.app/'
      target='_blank'
      class='text-sm md:text-base hover-underline-animation-widget'>LIVE</a
    >
  </div>
  <div
    class='absolute bg-gray-800 w-screen inset-0 z-0 origin-bottom'
    id='courtin'>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hover-underline-animation-widget {
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    color: #f3f4f6;
  }

  .hover-underline-animation-widget::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    transform: scaleX(0);
    height: 2px;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    background-color: #f3f4f6;
    transform-origin: bottom right;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease-out;
  }

  .hover-underline-animation-widget:hover::after {
    transform: scaleX(1);
    transform-origin: bottom left;
  }

  html {
    scrollbar-color: #f3f4f6 #baccfc;
  }
</style>

<script>
  import anime from 'animejs/lib/anime.es.js'

  anime({
    targets: '#courtin',
    scaleY: [1, 0],
    duration: 700,
    easing: 'easeInExpo',
  })
</script>
